<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>受験情報レポート 2027年度入試版</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #f8f6f1;
  --ink: #18160f;
  --dim: #7a7568;
  --rule: #d8d4c8;
  --paper: #fdfcf9;
  --c1: #1e3d72;
  --c2: #7a1818;
  --c3: #1a4d2e;
  --c4: #6b3a00;
  --c5: #3d1f6e;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.85;
  padding: 40px 20px 80px;
}
.page { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* ─ ヘッダー ─ */
.site-header { border-top: 4px solid var(–ink); padding-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.header-eyebrow { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.2em; color:var(–dim); margin-bottom:10px; }
h1 { font-family:‘Noto Serif JP’,serif; font-size:26px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.45; margin-bottom:8px; }
.header-sub { font-size:13px; color:var(–dim); border-top:1px solid var(–rule); padding-top:10px; margin-top:10px; display:flex; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; }

/* ─ 注意 ─ */
.callout { padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:28px; font-size:13px; line-height:1.75; border-left:3px solid; }
.callout.warn { background:#fffbeb; border-color:#d4a017; color:#6b4c00; }

/* ─ 共通日程バナー ─ */
.common-banner { background:var(–ink); color:#fff; padding:18px 24px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr)); gap:12px 24px; margin-bottom:48px; }
.cb-item label { display:block; font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.18em; opacity:.55; margin-bottom:4px; text-transform:uppercase; }
.cb-item span { font-family:‘Noto Serif JP’,serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; }

/* ─ カードシステム ─ */
.univ-section { margin-bottom:52px; }
.section-tag { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px; }
.tag-num { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.15em; padding:3px 10px; background:var(–ink); color:#fff; }
.tag-label { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.15em; font-weight:500; padding:3px 10px; border:1px solid currentColor; }
.card { border:1px solid var(–rule); background:var(–paper); overflow:hidden; }
.card-top { padding:20px 24px 18px; border-bottom:1px solid var(–rule); border-left:5px solid; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; gap:8px; align-items:start; }
.univ-name { font-family:‘Noto Serif JP’,serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.3; }
.dept-name { font-size:13px; color:var(–dim); margin-top:3px; }
.exam-date-badge { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:12px; padding:6px 12px; border:1px solid currentColor; white-space:nowrap; text-align:center; line-height:1.4; }
.card-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; border-bottom:1px solid var(–rule); }
@media(max-width:580px){ .card-grid,.card-top{ grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
.grid-col { padding:18px 22px; }
.grid-col+.grid-col { border-left:1px solid var(–rule); }
.col-title { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(–dim); padding-bottom:8px; border-bottom:1px solid var(–rule); margin-bottom:12px; }
.row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; gap:8px; padding:5px 0; border-bottom:1px dotted var(–rule); font-size:13px; }
.row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.row-label { color:var(–dim); font-size:12px; flex-shrink:0; }
.row-val { font-weight:500; text-align:right; }
.row-val.big { font-family:‘Noto Serif JP’,serif; font-size:17px; font-weight:700; }

/* ─ アクセス ─ */
.access { padding:18px 22px; background:#f3f1eb; border-bottom:1px solid var(–rule); }
.access-title { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(–dim); margin-bottom:14px; }
.route-wrap { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center; gap:4px; margin-bottom:10px; }
.stop { background:var(–ink); color:#fff; font-size:12px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; white-space:nowrap; }
.leg { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; padding:0 4px; font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:10px; color:var(–dim); gap:1px; }
.leg-line { width:36px; height:1px; background:var(–dim); position:relative; }
.leg-line::after { content:’’; position:absolute; right:-1px; top:-3px; border-left:5px solid var(–dim); border-top:3px solid transparent; border-bottom:3px solid transparent; }
.route-label { font-size:11px; color:var(–dim); margin-bottom:6px; margin-top:10px; }
.access-note { font-size:12px; color:var(–dim); line-height:1.7; margin-top:8px; }

/* ─ 現地TIPS ─ */
.tips-section { padding:18px 22px; }
.tips-title { font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(–dim); margin-bottom:14px; }
.tip-item { display:flex; gap:10px; padding:8px 0; border-bottom:1px dotted var(–rule); font-size:13px; line-height:1.65; }
.tip-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.tip-icon { flex-shrink:0; width:20px; text-align:center; margin-top:1px; }
.tip-text b { font-weight:700; }

/* ─ フッター ─ */
footer { margin-top:60px; padding-top:18px; border-top:1px solid var(–rule); font-size:11px; color:var(–dim); line-height:1.85; }

/* カラー */
.c1{color:var(–c1);} .c2{color:var(–c2);} .c3{color:var(–c3);} .c4{color:var(–c4);} .c5{color:var(–c5);}
.bl1{border-color:var(–c1);} .bl2{border-color:var(–c2);} .bl3{border-color:var(–c3);} .bl4{border-color:var(–c4);} .bl5{border-color:var(–c5);}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

<header class="site-header">
  <p class="header-eyebrow">EXAM SCHEDULE &amp; ACCESS GUIDE — 2027 ENTRANCE · 5 SCHOOLS</p>
  <h1>志望校 受験情報レポート<br><span style="font-size:18px;font-weight:400;">試験日・会場・アクセス・現地注意事項</span></h1>
  <div class="header-sub">
    <span>対象：2027年度入試（令和9年度）</span>
    <span>前期日程基準</span>
